Review of Anhoplocampa Wei (Hymenoptera, Tenthredinidae), with description of a new species and a new combinationAbstract Anhoplocampa is redescribed based on new material. Anhoplocampa bicoloricornis sp. n. from China is described. Anhoplocampa yunanensis (Haris & Roller, 1999), comb. n. is transferred from Trichiocampus. A key to species of Anhoplocampa is provided. The differences between Anhoplocampa and Trichiocampus Hartig, 1837, Priophorus Dahlbom, 1835, Hoplocampa Hartig, 1837 and Renonerva Wei & Nie, 1998 are briefly discussed.